data.description: Come & See this beautiful Townhouse Unit today! Built in 2003, this open floor plan home features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths on 1628 sqft in the desirable Ashley River Commons Neighborhood. The neighborhood offers a community Pool, a Clubhouse and its own boat ramp and dock on the Ashley River! The fenced in backyard offers lots of space, shade and privacy surrounded by trees and backing up to a wooded area. The inside offers freshly painted walls and new LVL flooring in a beautiful wood design. The combined living/dining room is spacious and full of sunlight. Additionally, master bedroom with private bathroom and two bedrooms with shared hallway bathroom.
